OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F335A1783521459
OL,3,CFamily of Leeds United superfan who
OL,4,Cvanished on way to World Cup 'worried
OL,5,Csick'
OL,7,FThe family of a Leeds United superfan
OL,8,Fwho 'vanished without a trace' when
OL,9,Ftravelling to the USA for the World
OL,10,FCup say they are 'worried sick'.
OL,12,FMichael Hewitt, who is known to many
OL,13,Fas 'Little Mick', had been travelling
OL,14,Ffrom Leeds to Boston for the World Cup
OL,15,Fvia Barcelona on Saturday 20 June.
OL,17,FHis family say their last contact with
OL,18,Fhim was a text message when he was in
OL,19,FBarcelona in the early hours of Sunday
OL,20,F21 June.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,336,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F335A1783521459
OL,3,CFamily of Leeds United superfan who
OL,4,Cvanished on way to World Cup 'worried
OL,5,Csick'
OL,7,FMichael, who hasn't missed a Leeds
OL,8,FUnited game in around 40 years, has
OL,9,Fnot been heard from since.
OL,11,FHis family believe he never made it to
OL,12,FBoston and may still be in Spain.
OL,14,FHis sister, Janet McCluskey, said:
OL,15,F"We're worried sick. We can't get on
OL,16,Fwith our normal lives because at the
OL,17,Fmoment we're out of our minds with
OL,18,Fworry and can't eat or sleep.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,336,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F335A1783521459
OL,3,CFamily of Leeds United superfan who
OL,4,Cvanished on way to World Cup 'worried
OL,5,Csick'
OL,7,F"We're worried to death thinking that
OL,8,Fhe may be laying injured somewhere or
OL,9,Fworse.
OL,11,F"We just need some confirmation that
OL,12,Fhe's fine or on his way back. We just
OL,13,Fwant to know that he's okay."
OL,15,FMichael's brother, Gary Hewitt, says
OL,16,FMichael's phone has been out of
OL,17,Fservice since then and he hasn't
OL,18,Fposted any updates on social media.
OL,20,FHe said: "He vanished without a trace.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,336,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F335A1783521459
OL,3,CFamily of Leeds United superfan who
OL,4,Cvanished on way to World Cup 'worried
OL,5,Csick'
OL,7,F"Football is his life, it's his
OL,8,Fpassion and his hobby. Everything
OL,9,Frevolves around football and his
OL,10,Ffootball friends.
OL,12,F"That's why it's so worrying that he's
OL,13,Fgoing off to see England and losing
OL,14,Fcontact with his mates."
OL,16,FMichael has been reported missing and
OL,17,FInterpol have been alerted.
OL,19,FHis family are asking anyone who has
OL,20,Fhad any contact with Michael since he
OL,21,Fwent missing to get in touch.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
